snippet.title: Loopwood - Gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Gameplay of Loopwood, a jam game developed in 5 days during Spellkollektivet Halloween Game Jam 2023 for playdate.

Team:
Bartosz Stochel: Code & Music
Sebastian Jelen: Code
Filip Loster: Code & Design
Leene Kunnap: Art

Check it out:
https://aare.itch.io/loopwood
